01:05:55.830 --> 01:05:57.582
the way Rhaenys
thinks of Daemon.

971
01:05:57.707 --> 01:05:59.583
Daemon believes that
he's. of course.

972
01:05:59.584 --> 01:06:00.584
completely in the right

