to have humor.</i>

988
01:06:28.905 --> 01:06:30.030
<i>And when I first saw</i>

989
01:06:30.031 --> 01:06:31.573
what Tom Glynn-Carney
was doing with Aegon.

990
01:06:31.574 --> 01:06:33.867
