where I didn't know it existed."

991
01:06:33.868 --> 01:06:35.077
<i>And it's painful.</i>

992
01:06:35.078 --> 01:06:36.704
<i>a guy who's way
in over his head.</i>

993
01:06:36.705 --> 01:06:38.122
