what he does.

996
01:06:42.460 --> 01:06:44.629
SPEAKER 2: Aegon
the Magnanimous.

997
01:06:44.796 --> 01:06:46.381
Hail King Aegon!

998
01:06:47.257 --> 01:06:48.633
The Magnanimous?

999
01:06:50.468 --> 01:06:52.761
I think Aegon is
the kind of father

1000
01:06:52.762 --> 01:06:55.640
