because he finds it funny.

1001
01:06:55.765 --> 01:06:56.766
<i>He loves his kids.</i>

1002
01:06:56.891 --> 01:06:58.267
<i>I have no doubt about that.</i>

1003
01:06:58.268 --> 01:06:59.601
<i>He loves his kids dearly.</i>

1004
01:06:59.602 --> 01:07:02.229
<i>But he's not one
to discipline them.</i>

1005
01:07:02.230 --> 01:07:04.149
If anything. he's. you know.

1006
01:07:04.274 --> 01:07:05.607
